Title: Dataset_name
Author: Report_Author

IsOfficial: Indicates if row is program estimate. 1 indicates is program estimate.
ShortName: Short name for publication that is displayed in the publication filter
Title: Name of study
Author: Author(s) of the report
VariableOMDolPerMwh: Variable operating and maintenance costs dollars per megawatts
FixedOMDolPerKw: Fixed operating and maintenance costs dollar per kilowatts
lcoe: Calculated Levelized Cost Of Energy value
OnghtCptlCostDolPerKw: Overnight capital cost dollar per kilowatt
AvailabilityFactor: Percentage of time capacity is available e.g. not unavailable due to planned or unplanned outtages
PvAxis: PV axis - Fixed, 1 axis or 2 axis
CspStorageHours: CSP - number of hours of storage at full capacity
MktTypeComResUtility: Indicates Market type.  eg. commercial, residential, utility
ResourceQuality1: Resource quality for renewable energy - describes wind and solar by class
ResourceQuality2: Secondary resource characterization. Currently used only for onshore and offshore wind
PvCurrentAcOrDc: Photovoltaic current is either AC or DC
ContingencyFactor: Multiplication factor to original overnight capital cost allow for contingency
OnghCptCstDlKwInclCtng: Overnight capital cost dollar per kilowatt including contingency
LearningFactor: Reduction in capital due to learning - will generally be less than 1.0
OMAllInclusive: All inclusive operating and maintenance costs.
Leadtimeyears: Number of years required to build - check if includes planning
Co2MetricTonsPerMwh: how much CO2 generated  in metric tons per megawatt hours
DtstTypMdlMktEngnrgPgm: Dataset type.  Values: Engineering, Field Data, Market Analysis, Model, Program
DolYear: Year in which dollar price is given
DataVintageYearNote: Notes for Data Vintage Year field
PublicationNotes: Notes on the publication
OnghCptCstDlKwInclCtngNote: Notes on the publication
FuelNote: Notes for Overnight Capital Cost field
HeatRateNote: Notes for all OM (Operating and maintenance) fields
GeneralCostsNote: Notes for Heat Rate field
GeneralHeatRateEffNote: Notes for cost fields
AvgCapacityFactorNote: Notes about the study
OnghtCptlCostDolPerKwNote: Notes for overnight capital cost field
